Module: header
Description: Persistent navigation header (auth-aware, user display, login/logout)

========================================
1. config.js - Add module configuration
========================================

Open: vite/src/config.js
Add in MODULE_CONFIG:

header: {
  path: null,
  container: 'header',
  authorization: null,
  persistent: true,
  priority: 1,
  init: null
}

Note: priority: 1 ensures header loads before other modules
